# Optional: used by `pnpm seed-env` to pre-populate the vault.
# After seeding, these values live inside ./data/vault.enc and .env is no longer read.
#
# FOLDER_ID  = UUID used to list / delete docs in that folder
# FOLDER_PATH = slash-separated folder name path used as import target (Omni requires path, not id)

